    "description": {
      "value": "<p><b>Source</b> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 18</em>, <em>Rise of the Runelords Player's Guide pg. 11</em>, <em>Curse of the Crimson Throne Player's Guide pg. 13</em>, <em>Pathfinder Campaign Setting pg. 209</em>, <em>Inner Sea World Guide pg. 290</em>, <em>Adventurer's Armory pg. 0</em>, <em>Varisia, Birthplace of Legends pg. 14</em></p><h3><span title=\"PFS Legal\">[PFS]</span> Statistics</h3><p><b>Cost</b> 40 gp <b>Weight</b> 14 lbs.</p><p><b>Damage</b> 1d10 (small), 2d6 (medium); <b>Critical</b> x3; <b>Range</b> -; <b>Type</b> B; <b>Special</b> -</p><p><b>Category</b> Two-Handed; <b>Proficiency</b> Martial</p><p><b>Weapon Groups</b> Hammers</p><h3>Description</h3><p>The crude metal of this massive hammer's head ends in multiple blunt spikes that help concentrate the force of a powerful swing down into a smaller, more focused area, allowing it to smash through armor with greater ease. Due to the tremendous size and weight of its head, an earth breaker is poorly balanced, and requires two hands to properly lift and control.</p>"
